**Don&#39;t use `var`** in React.

`tempLogin` is always re-initialized for every re-render to

```
{
    login: &quot;&quot;,
    password: &quot;&quot;
}
```

Thus, `tempLogin.login` is always `&quot;&quot;`.

Instead, have your `useState()` as:

```
React.useState({
    login: &quot;&quot;,
    password: &quot;&quot;
